  {% else %}
  <p class="body-text">For the mobile app I first created paper wireframes to test different approaches for the booking flow. The best ideas were then transferred to digital wireframes. The focus was on a fast, simple process — based on Jonas's needs: a clear search function with filtering options, so he reaches the right therapist without detours.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>

