  {% else %}
  <p class="body-text">Based on the usability findings, the hi-fi prototype was developed. The colour concept is oriented around calm and trust: a dark sage green as primary colour, light neutral surfaces, clear typography. Each screen reflects a concrete design decision that emerged from research.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>

